  <md:abstract>By the end of this section, you will be able to:
<list>
<item>List the unifying characteristics of eukaryotes </item>
<item>Describe what scientists know about the origins of eukaryotes based on the last common ancestor</item>
<item>Explain endosymbiotic theory</item>
</list></md:abstract>
  <md:language>en</md:language>
